    "patch_code": "public Element clone() {\n    Element clone = (Element) super.clone();\n    clone.dataSet.clear(); // Clear all dataSets in order not to directly inherit from the parent\n    for(Map.Entry<String, String> entry : attributes().entrySet()) \n        clone.dataSet.put(entry.getKey(), entry.getValue()); // Replace every attribute one by one\n    clone.id(\"\"); // Clear id since it is unique to elements\n    clone.className(\"\"); // Clean up class names since they can change over time\n    return clone;\n}",
